item.title: Please help me out
item.dc:creator: @93dcthugs93 93dcthugs93
item.description:
@93dcthugs93 wrote:

Make sure you have the updated Java. If you still can’t connect then, make sure you have the correct Port filled in & you’ve got the IP typed correctly.

If you still can’t connect make sure you have Hamachi if the server requires Hamachi. You can find a guide to Hamachi stickied on the top of this forum your in now.
